Package: markovmix
Type: Package
Title: Mixture of Markov Chain with Support of Higher Orders and Multiple Sequences
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: 
    person(given = "Xiurui",
           family = "Zhu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zxr6@163.com",
           comment = NULL)
Maintainer: Xiurui Zhu <zxr6@163.com>
Description: Fit mixture of Markov chains of higher orders from multiple sequences. It is also compatible with ordinary 1-component, 1-order or single-sequence Markov chains. In addition to the fit function, custom print and predict functions are also provided.
